Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.93,0:01:34.46,Top,,0,0,0,,A midnight feast...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.46,0:01:36.03,Top,,0,0,0,,A lacrosse match...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.03,0:01:41.35,Top,,0,0,0,,We thought that the days of the first form \Nat St. Clare's consisted of nothing but fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.14,0:01:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A sudden major incident struck!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.99,0:01:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We found out that it was Kathleen \Nwho's been stealing money from everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.48,0:01:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a huge shock!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.24,0:01:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kathleen only did it because she wanted so desperately to buy presents and make us happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.24,0:01:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the past now! {lit: we've forgotten already}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.52,0:01:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kathleen swore to never do it again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.88,0:02:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{One-two...}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.56,0:02:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a morning jog!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.66,0:02:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's beautiful!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.67,0:02:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What for?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.24,0:02:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You never turned away from me, \Nbut treated me just the same, even after all I’d done.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.55,0:03:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still worried about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.07,0:03:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You slipped up, took a wrong turn—\Nit could happen to anyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.52,0:03:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But to forgive and forget\Nis what true friendship all about!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.39,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that our friendship only grew stronger instead because of that incident.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.57,0:03:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I also like Kathleen even more than before now!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we are friends, you still need to earn your place on the team. {lit: but the seat of a lacrosse player is a different thing - meaning "we're friends, but that doesn't mean I'll let you have my place on the team", maybe: "Friends notwithstanding, you will still have to earn my lacrosse spot. "}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kathleen, Isabel, in the next match, \NI'll be on the field!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.68,0:03:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.74,0:03:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.60,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How did that happen? {/what do I do}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.09,0:03:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring it back to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.18,0:03:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I just wanted \Nto let some fresh air into the room.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.16,0:04:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy, were you studying all night long?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.66,0:04:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I got carried away and lost track of time. {lit: I suddenly entered passion}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.18,0:04:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Why don't I treat you \Nto some cinnamon tea as a thank you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.17,0:04:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible! I wonder how many years \Nit would take to read it all?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.56,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there's a photo of Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.40,0:04:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Society in Hellas—an approach through the Greek myth." {futatsu no kousatsu actually means "Two considerations" and idk how "society in hellas" became that}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy's paper is in a magazine?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.57,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a famous magazine!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Miss Kennedy, who teaches history \Nat St. Clare's School,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.44,0:04:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is an excellent researcher with two degrees..."
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.56,0:04:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We had no idea you were such \Nan accomplished academic, Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.53,0:04:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were me, I’d be talking about it \Non every street corner! {lit: if it were me, I'd spread it all over the city}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.99,0:04:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.92,0:04:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Studying and writing papers \Nare two things I can never get enough of. {actually "essays" but I think she means papers}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible! {lit: respect}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.86,0:05:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In the classroom, I try to share with the children all I’ve learnt up to now, with all my heart. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.07,0:05:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I made an oath the other day, \Nwhen Janet brought fire-cracks to the classroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.47,0:05:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"I will conduct marvelous lessons, for the girls." {lit: for everyone's sake, ...}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really sorry for that time... {lit: that time, really - assuming "sorry"}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.21,0:05:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember, when I was your age...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.78,0:05:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to study history \Nat Oxford University.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,At Oxford University?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.09,0:05:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She's kind...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.97,0:05:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a trace of self-importance... {lit: about herself, doesn't show off at all}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy truly is the best kind of teacher...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.61,0:05:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.56,0:05:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And so... That's why Louis XVI was...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.65,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! We covered this last week, didn't we? \NNow, where was it...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.07,0:05:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If only her classes were good too... {???? lit: this was good for a lesson}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.08,0:06:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No offense, but her voice is like a lullaby to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.87,0:06:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an interesting class, \Nbut only if you listen really closely... {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hilary.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.97,0:06:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that the second formers \Nalso bully Miss Kennedy like we used to?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.48,0:06:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They give her no quarter. {lit: it looks cruel}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.78,0:06:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They ask her weird questions, \Nswap her chalk for fake ones...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.03,0:06:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And call her "Old Kenny." {from book, in JP it's Old Kenny}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe that? \NSo crude!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.02,0:06:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all the things you used to do yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! This is serious, people!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.23,0:06:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first such incident \Nin the history of St. Clare's!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Mam'zelle...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.04,0:06:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mam'zelle?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught a cold!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They say French class tomorrow is cancelled!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.96,0:06:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait, that's not all. {lit: listen to the end}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.59,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of French, we’ll be having \Na joint class with the second form!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,With the second form?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.58,0:07:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And which teacher do you think will be taking it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.14,0:07:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy will be taking the joint class?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.17,0:07:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the second form, will have to attend Old Kenny’s \Nclass tomorrow together with the first form.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.76,0:07:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we put our plan on hold, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.18,0:07:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not! \NWe'll carry it out as planned.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.91,0:07:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look. Remember what Old Kenny \Nhates the most in the world?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.52,0:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A cat?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.32,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Tomorrow will be fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls, I’m sure we’ll have a splendid lesson today, seeing how the first
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.50,0:07:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and second forms have filled \Nthis classroom so peacefully together. {lit: since the 1st and 2nd year got along in lining up}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.80,0:07:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a new experience for me, \Nbut I'm going to do my best to teach you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing? {lit: what happened, senpai? - can't call them seniors, can't call them senpai, also it's not exactly why are you laughing but just general "what's the matter [with that giggle]?"}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.30,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing for you pipsqueaks to worry about. {lit: it's not related to little-chan}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.57,0:08:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipsqueaks?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, open your textbooks to page 90...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy! We're scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.20,0:08:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'll see what it is. \NYou all calm down now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.09,0:08:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Somebody! Take it away! {ano neko wa?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm allergic to cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.85,0:08:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.68,0:09:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.35,0:09:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Take it away!\NI'm allergic to cats! No!" {???? before it was ano neko wa but here it's some koucha ikou - nc what it could be}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.36,0:09:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you think she's gonna tell Headmistress?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Kenny won't get mad \Nno matter what we do!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How awful!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.59,0:09:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?\NI've run away again.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.83,0:09:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.83,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.67,0:10:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Oh no... {chotto}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mam'zelle!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.06,0:10:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mam'zelle! You have a cold, \Nwhat on earth are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.17,0:10:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I’m practising to ride a bicycle. \NThat’ll certainly blow the cold away. {first word is hora which is something like "What do you think it looks like?"}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.21,0:10:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to take today’s classes properly, \Nbut Headmistress made me take the day off!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.90,0:10:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please support from behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.12,0:10:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there she is.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.74,0:11:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So? I’m a quick learner, aren’t I?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.63,0:11:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.21,0:11:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to cycle to school \Ntogether with my students in no time!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.15,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's what you're practising for?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.12,0:11:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a challenge from life! \NEverything is a challenge! {lit: Human challenge}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're incredible, Mam'zelle!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bush! \NSlow me down! {????? jama yo = obstacle - think she means "there's an obstacle on the way"; second part sounds like odokinasai - no clue what it could be, maybe stop me, maybe don't let go}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to turn yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.65,0:11:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.98,0:11:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really enough to get you so impressed?! {??????? lit: over something this little, you raise your eyes - usually that'd mean "you roll your eyes/give up" but there was nothing for kenny to give up??? I assume she refers to kenny saying "it's incredible" so like "are you really that impressed by something so simple?"}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mam'zelle,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.76,0:11:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,i-it's a marvellous feat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Compared to you,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a failure of a teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.80,0:11:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,a fraud. {petenshi = swindler; imposter; crook}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A fraud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy, what do you mean \Nwhen you say you're a fraud?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.77,0:12:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I say that because I simply can't \Nteach my students properly.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.49,0:12:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't ever finish a class, \NI'm getting paid for nothing. {/don't tell them anything}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm but a fraud.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.17,0:12:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't quit now, \NI will only be a burden. {/if I keep trying to be a teacher}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't believe my ears!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do, \Nwhining like that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.68,0:12:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be more...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.62,0:12:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,assertive! {forward-looking; positive}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.69,0:12:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don’t have the same sort \Nof strong backbone as you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you acting like a child in your age?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.68,0:12:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am a child!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.73,0:12:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Weakling! {/Wimp}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And a weakling too!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're a weakling,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.22,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,how come you're so stubborn?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, quit! {this job}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.17,0:12:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This job, filled with love, \Nemotion and pride, is not for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Then quit I will! {/I'll quit then}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiens! Were you girls eavesdropping?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.22,0:13:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.19,0:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy is an amazing teacher! \NShe's the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.91,0:13:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That much I already know!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She's kind...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.41,0:13:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and excellent?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.68,0:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's considerate...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and humble!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do know!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.80,0:13:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But she has a different path in life. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.00,0:13:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Different path?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.91,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tant pis! That's a secret. {??? trusting chatgpt on this}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret? What is it? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.12,0:13:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Regardless, w-we're in no position \Nto discuss this issue!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.13,0:13:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The important choices in life \Nare for one to make oneself.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.62,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of the rules of being a human! {??? lit: rule as a human}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rules of being a human?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.56,0:13:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Miss Kennedy really does quit...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.99,0:14:05.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,I do want to become a good teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.98,0:14:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Pat.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.75,0:14:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And Isabel.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy! Please don't quit!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.79,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.66,0:14:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We think you're a wonderful person, \Nmore confident than anyone else! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.53,0:14:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We think you should puff out your chest and hold your head high, as the greatest teacher at St. Clare’s! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.12,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll avenge you—by thumping those haughty second formers in a game of lacrosse! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.38,0:14:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat, Isabel...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.93,0:14:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.55,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mam'zelle!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.52,0:14:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.83,0:14:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel, get in here!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if we talk for a minute? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.04,0:14:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing major, though... {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.69,0:14:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to take some advice? {??????????????????? no clue what's this anpu}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.79,0:14:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.71,0:14:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there was a time \Nwhen I didn’t have any confidence either. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.16,0:15:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Students kept belittling me, \Nand I ended up sobbing every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.18,0:15:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But just one good opportunity \Nto show them their place is enough! {??????? lit: but with just chance; start; cue; excuse; motive; impetus; occasion, it's fine}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.41,0:15:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mam'zelle...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you need to adopt \Na disagreeable personality. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.88,0:15:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Become forward, like me. \NThen your students won't have... {impudent; shameless; brazen; forward; audacious; cheeky}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.36,0:15:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,anything to say! {gyafun = being argued into silence; being left speechless}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good evening, Mam'zelle...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't really mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to make Miss Kennedy quit?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you at the dorm at this hour?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.59,0:15:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not teaching others how to live their lives—\Nwasn't that one of the rules? { of being a human}{lit: don't talk about others' matters - I fail to see how that is relevant here?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.72,0:15:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,are there to be broken.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.78,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My, who is it this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.45,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kathleen!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.48,0:15:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So many guests here!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kathleen?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.35,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, there's something \NI'd like to discuss with you privately.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.26,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Seriously? \NThey kicked us out?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, that Kathleen...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How unfriendly! {stand-offish; distant; not frank; reserved}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.10,0:16:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I don't know if it's my place \Nto say something like this at all, but... {lit: saying this might be awfully impertinent}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.07,0:16:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I also had no self-confidence once!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.77,0:16:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always on edge, \Nafraid of falling out of everyone’s favour. {/to become hated by everyone}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially of Pat's and Isabel's.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.07,0:16:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we wouldn’t be able to be friends \Nif I showed them my bad side.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.09,0:16:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.04,0:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I messed up big time, those two said \Nthey only grew to love me even more.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.48,0:16:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I've learned to love myself too—\Nwhen I'm cheerful and gentle. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.97,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm proud to be friends with the twins.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.06,0:16:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to keep doing my very best, \Nto become an excellent girl, like Isabel and Pat!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.42,0:17:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I learned to look forward \Nto every single day! {lit: every day became unbelievably wonderful}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.79,0:17:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kathleen...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.10,0:17:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kathleen,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.70,0:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I admire you. {/you're amazing}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kathleen!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say to Miss Kennedy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a secret?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.19,0:17:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.15,0:17:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, thank you very much \Nfor coming here tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.18,0:17:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never felt like this before. {lit: this is my first night like this}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.68,0:17:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a teacher, \NI want to remain strict with myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.19,0:17:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't give even one good lesson,\NI don't deserve to keep this job.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.90,0:17:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try once again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? Remember the plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.51,0:18:01.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,If this lesson is a success, \NI'll stay at this school.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.22,0:18:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that Miss Kennedy might quit?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.85,0:18:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on the class she's giving right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.72,0:18:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.59,0:18:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like the second formers \Nwere plotting something again today.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please open page 90 of your textbooks.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.00,0:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Old Kenny somehow different today?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as usual. {??? unsure maybe "don't care/doesn't matter"}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.70,0:18:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.27,0:18:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One-two...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{??? think kenny is saying something but uhhh}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.52,0:18:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoo! Go away!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What... What an awful prank!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want? \NWe're having class! {lit: it's the middle of the class}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.08,0:18:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.67,0:18:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The twins who think themselves popular, \Nalways acting so high and mighty?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The stuck-up twins who're so full of themselves!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.56,0:19:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.61,0:19:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! They've never... {????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.21,Overlap,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, if it isn't the thief from the other day!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.31,0:19:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told the thief about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.78,0:19:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tessie!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.25,0:19:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You take those smearing words back at once! {literal: shaming words}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.74,0:19:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Be mindful of how others feel. {lit: don't hurt another's heart}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.53,0:19:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Respect what others take pride in. {lit: appreciate others' pride}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.23,0:19:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who forget this etiquette have no right \Nto sit and learn at the same desk as the others. {/as her friends}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.30,0:19:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To learn is to love.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.24,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about learning to love \Nyour friends and teachers.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.07,0:19:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To look at yourself from the outside—\Nthat takes courage! {???????? lit: reflect on your actons, from the bottom of your heart, have courage}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.11,0:19:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That, and so many other things, \Nwere what I wanted to teach you. But… {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the most important thing... {??? lit: the heart of thinking about others}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.22,0:19:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,being considerate to others—that I never managed to teach you, and that's what I'm ashamed of. {???? this episode is driving me crazy a bit}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The class is over.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.47,0:20:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy went to see Headmistress! \NShe's quitting St. Clare's!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.71,0:20:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmistress! Where's Miss Kennedy?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.17,0:20:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Left for London to complete the formalities.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For London?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.12,0:20:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Although she wanted to keep it \N{a secret }from the students,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.80,0:20:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact Oxford’s lab \Nhad invited her some time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.05,0:20:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oxford?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.08,0:20:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Miss Kennedy felt \Nthat she couldn't leave this school.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.51,0:20:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She loved too deeply our school, \Nand each and every one of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.26,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.79,0:21:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone! {mou dame = no use now}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're too late!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.36,0:21:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.49,0:21:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.45,0:21:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.19,0:21:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a great lesson!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.74,0:21:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.76,0:21:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forget what you said to us!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We have so much more to learn from you! {lit: please let us learn a lot more from you}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.78,0:21:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have so many of your lessons yet to attend! {lit: we want to receive more of your lessons }
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.02,0:21:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, miss!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.30,0:21:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't get on now, \Nthe train will leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.71,0:21:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Oxford you dreamed of will be out of reach! {lit: you won't go to your dreamed oxford}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.96,0:21:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go without me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.88,0:22:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I only dream \Nabout being a teacher at St. Clare's!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.91,0:22:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.40,0:22:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, girls. Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.30,0:23:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Isabel, don't you feel frustrated?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.37,0:23:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go to the circus we've been looking forward to!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.82,0:23:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.96,0:23:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that culprit who broke the glass \Nin the classroom is still at large,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.16,0:23:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's no reason \Nto cancel our excursion to the circus!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.71,0:23:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! \NHey, Isabel, let's go see it anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.06,0:23:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed! After all, we've already made a promise to Jimmy, the flying trapeze artist.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.53,0:23:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twins at St. Clare's:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.21,0:23:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Four Presents." {in the book next chapter is "the broken window"}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:03.79,Note,,0,0,0,,Episode 8 \NThe Four Presents {四つのプレゼント}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.32,0:24:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
